<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
    <script src="../../script/flexible_css.js"></script>
    <script src="../../script/flexible.js"></script>
    <title>订单详情</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/api.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/commonWindow.css"/>
    <style>
        html,body {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            min-height: 100%;
            background: #F5F5F5;

        }
        ul li {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 44px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 0.4rem 0.267rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background: #fff;
        }
        ul li:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            top: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: #F5F5F5;
            transform: scaleY(.4);
        }
        .user-icon{
            width:1.227rem;
            height:1.227rem;
            border-radius:50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-right: 0.267rem;
        }
        .user-icon img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .user-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .item-key {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 2.453rem;
            font-size:14px;
            color:#333333;
        }
        .gray-value,.black-value{
            font-size:14px;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .gray-value {
            color:#999999;
            
        }
        .black-value {
            color:#333333;
        }
        .copy {
            font-size:14px;
            color:#ff5c98;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .step{
            padding: 0.32rem 0.4rem;
        }
        .step-ul {
            margin-top: 0.32rem;
        }
        .step-ul p {
            margin-bottom: 0.213rem;
            font-size:12px;
            color:#999999;
        }
        .step-ul p span {
            color:#ff5c98;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
 <ul>
     <li>
         <div class="user-icon"><img src="../../icon/defaultHead.png" alt=""></div>
         <span class="user-name">请叫我妲姬</span>
     </li>
     <li>
         <span class="item-key">微信号</span>
         <div class="gray-value" >请叫我妲姬123</div>
         <div class="copy">复制</div>
     </li>
     <li>
         <span class="item-key">验证信息</span>
         <div class="black-value">哈喽小小蜜</div>
         <div class="copy">复制</div>
     </li>
     <li>
         <span class="item-key">价格</span>
         <div class="black-value">1200LB</div>
     </li>
     <li>
         <span class="item-key">购买时间</span>
         <div class="gray-value">2019.05.16 17:22:20</div>
     </li>
     <li>
         <span class="item-key">订单号</span>
         <div class="gray-value">177718992990</div>
     </li>
     <li>
         <div class="black-value">你已发送加好友申请</div>
     </li>
     <li>
         <div class="black-value">请叫我妲姬 已通过你的加好友申请，请尽快确认，系统在48小时后自动确认</div>
     </li>
     <li>
         <div class="gray-value">2019.05.18 17:22:20</div>
     </li>
 </ul>
<div class="step">
    <div class="black-value">加好友步骤</div>
    <div class="step-ul">
        <p>1、进入微信添加好友，复制微信号到搜索输入框，点击搜索</p>
        <p>2、向女神发送添加好友申请，申请的内容必须为以上的验证信息内容，如：丽柜123456</p>
        <p>3、发送申请后，请进入“<span>我-订单</span>”更新订单状态</p>
        <p>4、如女神没有及时通过您的申请，可以尝试多添加几次</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
